{"tid":2163434,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"公關災難 Deliveroo vs 渣哥","createTime":"2020-08-18T16:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T05:23:34.000Z","uid":364053,"like":7,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"55577c6d8853b89b685d6dc63dad466f4e3fd24d","tid":2163434,"uid":364053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T16:04:08.000Z","msg":"Deliveroo罷工冷處理 最後有埋警察<br />\n全世界切 先急急腳同啲外賣仔協議解決罷工<br />\n出聲明道歉但話自己冇報警<br />\n但再比人爆離地 仲涉嫌種族歧視<br />\n之後再出聲明再道歉<br />\n但只係話要提升自己溝通能力<br />\n<br />\n渣哥為咗博宣傳搞投票<br />\n完美示範功能組別 仲要block人禁聲<br />\n全世界切 再被人提及同其他黃店恩怨<br />\n初次道歉冇人接受<br />\n幾個鐘再前出聲明 認自己柒<br />\n再話比大家知點處理渣哥<br />\n成功將個焦點轉去block唔block 人<br />\n<br />\n邊間公司大鑊啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDeliveroo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n渣哥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0534d3b941f3a819b24d6dc1951258bd9b047edf","tid":2163434,"uid":364053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T16:20:32.000Z","msg":"係咪好難選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e434dd8e7767cdb1a7da513eb1d4d7d9947287","tid":2163434,"uid":183453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:23:34.000Z","msg":"睇多一個星期先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}